,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:38:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"392cd657d179707deca950818649935c0cc36262","tid":531701,"uid":105366,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:39:15.000Z","msg":"係最愛<br />\n<br />\n但唔係最激情嗰個。"},{"pid":"b7696f44c5c9a0f565fd1857a3783076365bef23","tid":531701,"uid":12363,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"f4fc82b44aa8972fbbe313988d3c338d60b19dd4","tid":531701,"uid":44322,"like":23,"dislike":4,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"c627e80103e3e5674b487dc4237b347bafee8f3c","tid":531701,"uid":158660,"like":0,"dislike":31,"score":-31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:12:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:35:48.000Z","msg":"第一次就好笑<br />\n第二次就無聊<br />\n第三次就on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:40:51.000Z","msg":"第一次已經on9"},{"pid":"19312f0a430e3de308ec36dc0769c96e08dfffdf","tid":531701,"uid":39463,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:41:07.000Z","msg":"係，佢係我人生的第一位"},{"pid":"d160cf62a3b192d8ae64aee62182b759ba73e7fe","tid":531701,"uid":104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"未結，但一定係我最愛果個，一定會同佢結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fea6e0b64f4020ad5dec3375057d2aa3acfa0458","tid":531701,"uid":105366,"like":27,"dislike":4,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:43:37.000Z","msg":"又係時候貼返呢篇野:<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">呢個係殘酷既現實。<br />\n<br />\n好多時你一生人最愛最passionate既嗰個人可能係ABCD入面其中一個。<br />\n但可惜喺你同ABCD其中一個一齊之時，你重未係一個有能力或懂得去成熟處理一段長久關係既人。<br />\n結果冇辦法將ABCD留下而只能刷身而過。<br />\n<br />\n而若干年後，到你已經係一個有能力或懂得去成熟處理一段長久關係既人之時，你與ABCD多數早已天各一方，各自有自己既生活，不相往來。而就算仍然有機會偶然相遇，因各自早已分開走得太久太遠，兩人既際遇早已天南地北，沒有再能成為一對既條件或自由。<br />\n<br />\n就在此時，讓你遇上EFGH。<br />\n縱使你對EFGH既愛或激情可能其實並唔及對ABCD咁深，但因為你已經太懂得去處理二人關係，所以EFGH就算唔係最Passionate嗰個，但你地都可以發展得好好，好穩定，好暢順。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後晌你安穩下來多年之後，有一日又比你再遇返ABCD。就算愛火重燃，但你已經afford唔起去放棄一段十幾年既關係。亦唔可以漠視另一半已為你所作出既犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n於是，你終於學到了愛係唔需要擁有。見到、或甚至只係知到心中所愛那人依然健在、依然快樂咁活著，已經心滿意足。<br />\n<br />\n人生，就係咁。就係咁無耐。<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"23ffa86f75c96050c87aba6209ed3a5c645cce7c","tid":531701,"uid":44646,"like":7,"dislike":8,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"c0c681efa25fa3d4976e6825edd755a233ab7ccb","tid":531701,"uid":146588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:08:07.000Z","msg":"老實講, 結左婚既你, <br />\n到底你地既另一半係咪你人生中最愛果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:47:38.000Z","msg":"唔係<br />\n<br />\n老婆客觀條件好好，算靚、入息高過我，同我屋企關係又好<br />\n而人人都覺得我好錫老婆<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但有時午夜夢迴，發夢見到既，都係舊愛<br />\n人生，就係咁無奈"},{"pid":"ea563e32498ff661d2dbeddb5e65b155015a1cdc","tid":531701,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"734f4c32ec47aeb36d7155c9db93ad0d08b67d02","tid":531701,"uid":74262,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:55:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f11d4a591b0ee1f4fff3202af2ff4fecbbf97f35","tid":531701,"uid":74262,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47502406579e12b1a87f2e1f59ec4a760b19a981","tid":531701,"uid":16870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d160cf62a3b192d8ae64aee62182b759ba73e7fe","tid":531701,"uid":104,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T06:42:16.000Z","msg":"未結，但一定係我最愛果個，一定會同佢結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T10:06:16.000Z","msg":"邊個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998cf4434a3a3c955068f1459a8b5485cbb1fb50","tid":531701,"uid":104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"47502406579e12b1a87f2e1f59ec4a760b19a981","tid":531701,"uid":16870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d